metadata.name: Fun in Space
metadata.description:
Violette Cici is a French/Australian digital collage artist. I found her on Twitter and was drawn to her collage style.

"I believe that each species has its own perspective which creates a unique reality. The more we can open ourselves to the idea that other realities different than our own exist, the faster we can accept new ideas and viewpoints â€“ and the richer our lives will be. This is an important part of my art."

This piece, Fun in Space, reminds me of my love for sci-fi, where the laws of physics, space, and time are not limited.

What do you see?
